Emperico Web App
=================

Introduction
------------
This is a Web application using the ZF2.

Installation
------------

1) Clone the repository from here
    git@git.riktamtech.com:kishor/emperico.git

2) Install the composer using below command
    curl -s https://getcomposer.org/installer | php

3) Install all dependecnies
    php composer.phar install

Setting the project
--------------------
1) Move the config/autoload/local.php.dist to  config/autoload/local.php
2) Modify local.php file


3) Move the config/autoload/phpSettings.local.php.dist to  config/autoload/phpSettings.local.php
4) Modify phpSettings.local.php file

5) Create a file "data/logs/logfile" for error logging
6) Change permissions for log file (sudo chmod 666 data/logs/logfile)

7) Make sure db is setup and all migrations are run
8) Move the config/autoload/db.local.php.dist to  config/autoload/db.local.php
9) Modify contents of db.local.php file
